<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-2708] PDDocument.removePage() deletes the last page regardless of parameter passed</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2708</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This can be easily reproduced using provided example &lt;br/&gt;
org.apache.pdfbox.examples.pdmodel.RemoveFirstPage that will delete the last page from document instead the first one.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I think this bug was introduced within the last 3 months as my older snapshot build worked fine.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12781637">PDFBOX-2708</key>
            <summary>PDDocument.removePage() deletes the last page regardless of parameter passed</summary>
