                                    <watches>3</watches>
                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14360651" author="radomirml" created="Fri, 13 Mar 2015 17:03:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I tracked this down to PDPageTree.remove() that was invoking COSArray.remove() which didn&apos;t work if page was indirectly referenced. Can be fixed using COSArray.removeObject() instead.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Pages were removed from the end of the document as the rest of PDPageTree.remove() was updating COSName.COUNT although removal from the dictionary actually failed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll send a pull request with a fix.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14360656" author="tilman" created="Fri, 13 Mar 2015 17:07:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Send a diff instead, attach it here. However I assume that this DID work some time ago, and wonder when this was lost, so more research is needed (testing old versions).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14360781" author="radomirml" created="Fri, 13 Mar 2015 17:49:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attaching fix diff.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Yes, this was working before. I think regression was made between Sep 17 last year (as I was using that build for some time) and Feb 22 (when I pulled from git to build an update).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14361128" author="tilman" created="Fri, 13 Mar 2015 21:26:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It probably happened around or on 22.10, when work on &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2423&quot; title=&quot;Page tree handling needs rewriting&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2423&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2423&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; was started. It was OK on 21.10, but not ok on 1.11.2014. (I had a more recent change in mind and didn&apos;t think that the bug had been in the code for so long). I&apos;ll commit your patch later (but not today).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14361161" author="radomirml" created="Fri, 13 Mar 2015 21:47:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sounds good. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14361865" author="jira-bot" created="Sat, 14 Mar 2015 15:53:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1666698 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1666698&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1666698&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2708&quot; title=&quot;PDDocument.removePage() deletes the last page regardless of parameter passed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2708&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2708&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2423&quot; title=&quot;Page tree handling needs rewriting&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2423&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2423&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: use removeObject() instead of remove() to delete a page from the tree, update count only when successful, by Radomir Mladenovic&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14361883" author="tilman" created="Sat, 14 Mar 2015 16:31:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Setting to resolved. Thank you for spotting the error and for the fix!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
